#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krdc; is a client application that allows you to view or even control the "
"desktop session on another machine that is running a compatible server."
msgstr ""
"&krdc; je klijent aplikacija koja Vam dopušta da pregledate ili čak "
"kontrolišete radnu površinu na drugoj mašini koja je pokrenuta kompatibilnim "
"serverom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You would typically use &krdc; with the &kde; <acronym>VNC</acronym> server "
"(&krfb;), which is also known as Krfb, since it closely matches the special "
"features of &krdc;."
msgstr ""
"Tipično ćete koristiti &krdc; sa &kde;  <acronym>VNC</acronym> serverom "
"(&krfb;), koji je također poznat kao Krfb, obzirom da se skoro podudara sa "
"specijalnim olikama &krdc;-a."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to start &krdc; from &konsole;, the command is "
"<userinput><command>krdc</command></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da pokrenete &krdc; iz &konsole;, komanda "
"je<userinput><command>krdc</command></userinput>."

